title: etnies France welcome Claude Lévy
description: Claude Lévy grew up skating in Paris, but now lives in Nice, the south of France . He is 21 year old, very talented on a skateboard and is a super nice kid to go skate or hang out with, go check his style in this welcome to the French team video part.
